            <title>[CASSANDRA-3255] Sstable scrub status persists in compactionstats after scrub is complete</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3255</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When scrubbing the sstables on a node, the &apos;Scrub&apos; info persists in the &apos;compactionstats&apos; nodetool utility, even after the scrub is complete.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
